# Title: Suspicious Regsvr32 Execution From Remote Share
# Author: Nasreddine Bencherchali (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2022-10-31
# Level: high
# Description: Detects REGSVR32.exe to execute DLL hosted on remote shares
# MITRE Tactic: Uncategorized
# Tags: attack.stealth, attack.t1218.010
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/process_creation/proc_creation_win_regsvr32_remote_share.yml

CommandLine="* \\\\*" Image="*\\regsvr32.exe" OR OriginalFileName="\\REGSVR32.EXE"